window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Superheroes, dragons, and wizards - oh my!&nbsp;</p> <p>Fueled by Sam's unique superpower (that treats him like a video game, character with more levels to gain, and quests to fulfill), he and his party of beautiful heroines continue onward to bring peace to the fantastical expansion world of Galandia.&nbsp;</p> <p>Unfortunately, the evil in this land threatens a civil war that could lay waste not only to Galandia, but to Earth itself. But, if Sam can grind harder, loot more, and gather enough powerful allies, there's a small chance that not only can he stop the war, but unlock a secret no one could expect: Godmode!&nbsp;</p> <p><b>Warning: </b>This audiobook contains dimension hopping, ravishing women, barbarian werebears, amazing magic, raising a pet dragon, and the ability to become the strongest person the universe has ever seen. Thatâ€™s right, we said universe.</p>"; 
